&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0px&quot;&gt;When a group of us calling
ourselves Occupy the Castro took over the Human Rights Campaign
(HRC) store on December 3&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#8230;&lt;/p&gt;&topic=" target="_share"></a></li>
